<space/><foreign xml:lang="fr"><rs type="pers" ana="n_95027" ref="#fk__p_43204"><AUCTOR>Ferdinand <seg type="spc">Brunot</seg></AUCTOR></rs>, Doyen de la <rs type="inst">Faculté des<lb/>
